headline: IBKR Q3 Deep Dive: New Products, International Expansion, and Crypto Initiatives Shape Outlook
summary: Electronic brokerage firm Interactive Brokers (NASDAQ:IBKR) reported revenue ahead of Wall Street’s expectations in Q3 CY2025, with sales up 21.2% year on year to $1.66 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $0.57 per share was 6.1% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
